4. Game Concept Specification  
The game was defined as a story-driven detective mystery system where the player acts as 
a detective solving multiple criminal cases. 
Each case includes: 
• Crime scene investigation  
• Suspect interrogation  
• Evidence collection  
• Logical deduction  
The final objective is to identify the correct suspect based on collected evidence. 
Core gameplay loop: 
Investigate → Collect evidence → Interrogate suspects → Analyze → Solve case
